    oc:differentia "upgrades Spring Boot 2.x applications to Spring Boot 3.x by updating parent POM versions, removing deprecated Java EE dependencies (JAXB), upgrading Java to 17/21, and orchestrating Jakarta namespace and Spring Security sub-migrations" ;
